data.description: Mother-In-Law Suite Special! This spacious 2,476sqft, 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence offers an additional 876sqft, 1 bedroom (+ bonus room), 1.5 bathroom living quarters perfect for elderly parents or older children. The Mother-In-Law Suite comes complete with it's own fully functional kitchen, laundry, living room, and attached garage. The main home is meticulously well-maintained as well. Whether it's the private backyard oasis, large rear deck perfect for summer nights, or the convenient proximity to all things Knoxville has to offer, this listing is one that the whole family will love!
